那不是Locke
That is not Locke.

13
00:00:50,571 --> 00:00:51,731
嗯 我知道
Yeah, I know.

14
00:00:52,531 --> 00:00:55,611
无论他是谁 他说他能把我们带出这该死的小岛
Whoever he is, he says he can get us off this damn island.

15
00:00:56,461 --> 00:00:57,591
