I can't leave.

16
00:00:58,501 --> 00:00:59,711
Sun还不知在岛上哪个角落呢
Sun could be here somewhere.

17
00:01:01,631 --> 00:01:02,331
好吧
Fine.

18
00:01:03,131 --> 00:01:06,061
