Jimmy...

26
00:02:04,031 --> 00:02:04,791
嗯
Mmm.

27
00:02:06,111 --> 00:02:07,011
你真是...
You are...

28
00:02:09,121 --> 00:02:10,711
太厉害了
unbelievable.

29
00:02:11,641 --> 00:02:12,401
嗯
Mmm.

30
00:02:12,861 --> 00:02:14,391
宝贝 你和我不分伯仲
You weren't too shabby yourself, darlin'.

31
00:02:14,521 --> 00:02:14,841
嗯
Mmm.

32
00:02:17,221 --> 00:02:17,751
宝贝?
Baby?

33
00:02:18,091 --> 00:02:18,751
嗯?
Yeah?

34
00:02:19,091 --> 00:02:20,911
9点的时候 你不是要和那个人碰头吗?
Aren't you supposed to meet that guy at 9:00?

35
00:02:21,321 --> 00:02:22,081
嗯 然后呢?
Yeah. So?

36
00:02:23,781 --> 00:02:24,701
现在是8点...
It's 8...

37
00:02:25,301 --> 00:02:26,111
42分
42.

38
00:02:28,481 --> 00:02:29,111
该死!
Damn it!

39
00:02:42,341 --> 00:02:44,341
我本来不想让你看见的
You weren't exactly supposed to see that.

40
00:02:44,561 --> 00:02:46,001
Jimmy 你拿这么多钱要干什么?
Jimmy, what are you doing with all that money?

41
00:02:47,131 --> 00:02:49,731
