This meeting is a potential investment.

42
00:02:49,861 --> 00:02:50,901
我们约定五五分账
We're going 50/50.

43
00:02:51,551 --> 00:02:53,191
那家伙想先看到钱
The guy wants to see the money upfront.

44
00:02:53,891 --> 00:02:56,751
别担心 不会太久的 我马上回来
Don't worry. It won't take long. I'll be right back.

45
00:02:57,311 --> 00:02:59,671
然后我们就去兜风... 喔
Me and you'll go for round... Whoa.

46
00:02:59,851 --> 00:03:00,881
离箱子远点
Step away from the case.

47
00:03:03,241 --> 00:03:04,141
别乱来 宝贝
Take it easy, honey.

48
00:03:04,571 --> 00:03:05,701
帅哥 有件事我得告诉你
Here's the thing, dimples.

49
00:03:06,301 --> 00:03:08,451
我知道骗子的花样 我前夫就是骗子
I can spot a con man. I'm married to one.

50
00:03:08,781 --> 00:03:10,631
所以我知道你们那些伎俩
So I know all about the pigeon drop.

51
