乖乖把枪放下 但如果你不放
and put that gun down. But if you don't,

70
00:03:56,811 --> 00:03:58,891
那么 我也有办法
well, then all I gotta do is say the magic work,

71
00:03:59,061 --> 00:04:00,321
让那扇门为我打开
and that door busts open.

72
00:04:02,111 --> 00:04:03,321
你真是个蹩脚的骗子
You're a lousy con man.

73
00:04:05,791 --> 00:04:06,501
Lafleur啊
Lafleur.

74
00:04:07,491 --> 00:04:08,351
"La"什么?
"La" what?

75
00:04:08,991 --> 00:04:09,901
警察! 把枪放下!
Police! Drop the gun!

76
00:04:14,021 --> 00:04:16,911
- 手背过来 - 我们进来得早了点儿吧?
- Behind your back. - Cuttin' it a little close, huh?

77
00:04:17,221 --> 00:04:18,241
实在没办法啊
Only way to cut it.

78
00:04:21,551 --> 00:04:22,831
把你的衣服穿起来 Jim
Put your damn clothes on, Jim.

79
00:04:23,361 --> 00:04:24,371
没问题 好搭档
You got it, partner.

80
00:04:24,681 --> 00:04:26,701
- 你是警察? - 惊讶吧
- You're a cop? - Surprise.

81
00:04:26,921 --> 00:04:27,801
走吧 快走
Let's go. Move.

82
00:04:33,921 --> 00:04:41,801

迷失 第6季第8集

83
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,870
你就住在这里?
Is this where you lived?

84
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:22,690
嗯
Yeah.

85
00:05:25,770 --> 00:05:26,540
那是什么?
What is that?

86
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:32,530
它是我的一切
It's all I had.

87
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:37,360
嗯 各位 听我说!
All right, everybody, listen up!

88
00:05:38,490 --> 00:05:39,770
过来 围成圈
Come on in. Gather 'round.

89
00:05:42,290 --> 00:05:44,920
我知道你们都累极了
I know that everyone is tired.

90
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:46,640
我们度过了...
It was a...

91
00:05:47,730 --> 00:05:49,700
一个漫长而悲惨的夜晚
a long and traumatic night for all of us.

92
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:54,210
我知道 你们肯定满腹疑问
And you all have got a lot of questions, I know,

93
00:05:54,350 --> 00:05:56,540
我会尽力作答
And I will make myself available to answer them.

94
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,900
但现在 我们得继续出发
But right now we need to keep moving.

95
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,490
- 要抓住白天的优势 - 我们想知道
- We have to take advantage of the daylight. - We wanna know

96
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:03,780
留在寺庙的人都怎样了
what happened to the people who stayed behind at the temple.

97
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,810
黑烟杀了他们
The black smoke killed them.

98
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:15,780
嘿
Hey.

99
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:22,540
我知道那里发生的一切 可怕至极
I know that what happened back there was really scary.

100
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,640
但一切都结束了
But it's over.

101
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:28,730
你们和我在一起
You're with me now,

102
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:31,580
我承诺 会让大家相安无事的
and I promise that I'm gonna take care of you.

103
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:39,040
好了
Okay.

104
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,160
我们出发吧
Alright, let's move out.

105
00:06:53,450 --> 00:06:55,140
听上去 你这一晚上过得可不安生
Sounds like you had a hell of a night.

106
00:06:56,810 --> 00:06:57,410
没错
Yeah.

107
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:59,170
